channel.title: Rip off?
channel.description:
I'm gonna sell my xbox 360 console, no HDD to gamestop for 110$, since I've had no luck on craigslist.
Will I be getting ripped off? I don't ever play it anymore, but maybe there would be a better alternative.

item.title: Rip off?
item.dc:creator: @Fridder Fridder
item.description:
@Fridder wrote:

$110/$200 sounds like a good deal, and you still have the hard drive which could be sold for $10-$20 depending on your amount of space.
